1. *Vidiš* li ga tu? (Do you see him there?)
2. On *vidiše* da je veče. (He saw that it was evening.)
3. *Videćeš* kako ćeš biti zadovoljan. (You will see how you will be satisfied.)
4. *Vidimo* se za pola sata. (We will see each other in half an hour.)
5. *Videla* je da je u pravu. (She saw that she was right.)
6. *Videti* ćeš da sam u pravu. (You will see that I am right.)